{"pageProps":{"articleData":[{"pk_df_blog_page_id":126,"blog_content":"<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>Heroes of Jallianwala Bagh! You do not reside in our history books, just! You belong to\n                        our hearts!</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">The Jalliawala Bagh Massacre is still capable of sending down shivers through our spines. Be it\n                the merciless slaughter of innocent human lives or the acquittal of those guilty, this day is a</span>\n        <span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>black day for every Indian</strong>. Letâ€™s mark the</span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>102</strong></span><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 11px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><sup><strong>nd</strong></sup></span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>anniversary</strong></span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">of this event together by commemorating the lives of the martyrs, knowing more about this\n                day.</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>1)\n                                The Pinnacle of Casualties</em></strong></span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1xJk_eJoI2AT4poeg1Tw9bAbpc-qcKH9B\"\n                alt=\"undefined\" style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" /></div>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">There was only one narrow main entrance to the park. Furthermore, the park periphery was covered\n                with high walls which made it impossible for the people to climb and escape. This was the main reason\n                for the high number of casualties as the people were unable to evacuate the place in time. For saving\n                their lives, many people even tried jumping into the well to duck guns but eventually lost their\n                lives.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>2)\n                                No public gatherings allowed</em></strong></span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:none;\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1xqH2uiqeSZqAAULKMsWBj15Qr1gJs1xE\"\n                alt=\"undefined\" style=\"height: auto;width: 100%\" /></div>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">A</span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>Martian Law</strong></span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">was imposed on 12</span><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 11px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><sup>th</sup></span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">April 1919, because one of the English Missionary was attacked by an angry mob. Around\n                6,000-10,000 people were gathered in the park. But the public was</span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>never warned about any open fire</strong>.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>3)\n                                A friendly fiesta</em></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1LXxEllPCQ0qC4b3O2oxhBHJ7_c3s2EZS\" alt=\"undefined\"\n        style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" />\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">An annual fete of</span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>Baisakhi</strong></span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">was being celebrated by the local people. The people were unaware that an open shooting was going\n                to take place and were neither warned about it.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>4)\n                                Arms and Ammunitions</em></strong></span></p>\n<div style=\"text-align:none;\"><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1VUqGjPUWDp02VkI_1KCkzcLuw_oV02d7\"\n                alt=\"undefined\" style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" /></div>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">Apart from rifles, there were two cars filled up with machine guns. Around</span> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>1650 rounds were fired</strong>. The firing was only stopped when the soldiers ran out of\n                the rounds.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>5)\n                                Shaping the nation</em></strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=10xbIUpGlEokc2Bk1s8PAk1h0H_8sKEmH\" alt=\"undefined\"\n        style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" />\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">After the incident, many upcoming events related to freedom were sorted.</span> <a\n                href=\"https://www.mkgandhi.org/short/ev6.htm\" target=\"_blank\"><span\n                        style=\"color: rgb(235,107,86);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                        , sans;\"><strong>Gandhiji returned his 'Kaisar-i-Hind'</strong></span></a> <span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                , sans;\">medal and</span> <a\n                href=\"https://iniva.org/blog/2013/10/02/tagore-archive-the-letter-renouncing-his-knighthood/\"\n                target=\"_blank\"><span\n                        style=\"color: rgb(235,107,86);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                        , sans;\"><strong>Rabindranath Tagore renounced his knighthood</strong></span></a><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                , sans;\">. It was one of the reasons of the Non- Coorperation Movement to arise and come into\n                existence.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 16px;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>6)\n                                The revenge</em></strong></span> <br/><img\n                src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1A2vhMIW8bnnUERBtZNymXhS6jT7ths0_\" alt=\"undefined\"\n                style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" /></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">On 13th March 1940,</span> <span\n                style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><strong>Colonel Reginald Dyer</strong></span> <span\n                style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" , sans;\">was shot\n                dead by</span> <a\n                href=\"https://www.thebetterindia.com/95695/udham-singh-punjab-jallianwala-bagh-massacre/\"\n                target=\"_blank\"><span\n                        style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                        sans;\"><strong>Udham Singh</strong></span></a><span\n                style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" , sans;\">, member\n                of the revolutionist Ghadar party.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span\n                style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>7)</em></strong></span>\n        <span style=\"color: black;background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Verdana;\"><strong><em>A\n                                similar incident</em></strong></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1G9FUUsNfjM2SySYG1kuRxVSyLdtZjR5f\" alt=\"undefined\"\n        style=\"height: auto;width: auto\" />\n<p><span style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" , sans;\">A less known\n                massacre similar to the Jalliawala Bagh Massacre, known as the Qissa Khwani Bazaar Massacre took place\n                in Peshawar. It sparked due to the arrest of a prominent leader, Abdul Ghaffar Khan. On 23</span><span\n                style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 11px;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\"><sup>rd</sup></span> <span\n                style=\"color: black;background-color: white;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" , sans;\">April,\n                400 unarmed protestors were shot dead by the troops of British Government. It led to Khudai Khidmatagar\n                Movement.</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">Which fact did you have absolutely no clue about? Let us know in our</span> <a\n                href=\"https://www.instagram.com/desirefoundation/\" target=\"_blank\"><span\n                        style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                        , sans;\">Instagram handle!</span></a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(33,37,41);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\" ,\n                sans;\">Click here to know more such</span> <a\n                href=\"http://blog.desirefoundation.org/category?id=Untold%20Stories\" target=\"_blank\"><span\n                        style=\"color: rgb(0,123,255);background-color: transparent;font-size: 1.2rem;font-family: Open Sans\"\n                        , sans;\">Untold stories.</span></a>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\"></p>","blog_headline":"7 Confounding and Unlauded facts of the Jallianwala Bagh Massacre!","user_email":"arshleenkaurr@gmail.com","user_insta":"arshleen_kaur_","user_facebook":"","user_linkedin":"","user_name":"Arshleen Kaur","create_timestamp":"2021-04-13T02:34:53.000Z","header_img_path":"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1VaaBTudMJLNl_a0HKpeLBh49eFpgAiCs"}],"id":"126"},"__N_SSG":true}